Package edu.sru.thangiah.zeus.route

Class Summary
Attributes Contains all the infomation calculated by the cost functions
Depot Maintains information on the depots from which trucks service customers.
DepotLinkedList Contains instances of the Depot Class
Feasibility This class will determine at any time if the route is feasible.
PointCell Used to hold information on the customer or package that is to be delivered by a truck.
ProblemInfo Contains problem-specific information that may be used throughout Zeus.
Shipment Stores all of the information about a Shipment.
ShipmentLinkedList Maintains all of the Shipments of the VRP.
Truck Maintains information about the trucks
TruckLinkedList Maintains information about the trucks in the parent depot
TruckType Definition of a truck type
VisitNodesLinkedList Maintains all of the PointCells of a truck route.
